===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yŏu jiào wú lèi
===Etymology===
From the [[w:Analects of Confucius|Analects of Confucius]]
===Idiom===
'''[[有]][[教]][[無]][[類]]'''
# to provide education for all people without discrimination.
